# Android / Capacitor
# Keep the android project in git (it's a native project, not just build output)
# but ignore Gradle build artifacts
android/app/build/
android/.gradle/
android/captures/
android/local.properties
android/app/src/main/assets/public/

# Allow our documentation files through the *.md ignore
!README_ANDROID.md
!PORTING_REPORT.md
!TODO_NEXT.md
!src/mobile/adapters/README.md
!CURRENT_STATUS.md
!BRANDING.md
!BUILD_REPORT.md
!docs/github-repo-settings.md
!docs/REMOTE_RUNTIME.md
!docs/REMOTE_GIT_WORKFLOW.md
!docs/ANDROID_LLM_API_BRIDGE.md

# Package lock & generated gradle configs
